4) Display country name, city, and department name.
> select loc.country_id, loc.city, dep.department_name from locations loc, departments dep where loc.location_id = dep.location_id ; 
5) Display employee name and country in which he is working.
> select loc.country_id, emp.first_name from locations loc, employees emp where emp.department_id = loc.department_id ; 

